🔍 HOW TO SEE PATTERNS OVER TIME
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

When you have lots of entries, that's called DATA DENSITY! 📊

The MORE pings and colors you write down, the BETTER you can see patterns!

Think of it like this:
📏 1 day  = Just one dot
📏 1 week  = A line forming
📏 1 month = A SHAPE appearing!
📏 1 year  = The whole picture!

---

🎨 SCROLL YOUR COLORS INTO MOTION
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

Here's a cool trick! 🌀

Flip through your pages fast or scroll your notes. Watch the colors flow!

What you might see:
🌊 Waves of Orange  → Times you were wild and spontaneous
🌊 Waves of Blue    → Times you were thinking and planning
🌊 Waves of Green   → Times you were growing and learning

If it goes 🟠🟠🟠 → 🔵🔵🔵 → 🟢🟢🟢, that's a GRADIENT in motion!

The colors don't jump — they BLEND and FLOW from one to another.

This shows how YOU change over time, like a living painting! 🎨✨


