📐 THE GEOMETRY OF EMOTIONS
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

Your emotions and relationships have SHAPES! Look for them:

🔺 TRIANGLES
When three homies or three colors keep appearing together,
that's a TRIANGLE relationship!

Example: You + Homie A + Homie B = 🔺
If every time you all talk, the colors are 🟠🔵🟢,
you've found a stable triangle pattern!

🟢 CIRCLES
When the same mood keeps coming back, that's a CIRCLE!
Like: Happy → Curious → Thinking → Happy again
This is your emotional CYCLE!

📊 LINES
If your curiosity always follows a straight line,
like: Questions → Experiments → Answers → New Questions,
that's a LINEAR pattern!

💎 POLYGONS
When many friends connect in interesting ways,
you get complex SHAPES!
Maybe you're the center of a star ⭐
Or part of a chain 🔗
Or in a cluster of friends 🫧

The GEOMETRY shows you the STRUCTURE of your world!


