💰 THE FINANCE OF LEARNING
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

Think of your curiosity and energy like MONEY! 💵

You SPEND your energy on things. You INVEST in curiosity.

THE BUDGET:

⚡ ENERGY COST
Some things cost MORE energy:
• Hard puzzles cost 🔵🔵🔵 (lots of thinking!)
• Wild adventures cost 🟠🟠🟠 (lots of chaos!)
• Learning new skills cost 🟢🟢🟢 (lots of growth!)

💰 ENERGY INCOME
Some things GIVE you energy:
• Fun with friends gives you 🟠🟠 back!
• Discovering something new gives you 🟢🟢 back!
• Figuring something out gives you 🔵🔵 back!

📊 YOUR PROFIT
If you SPEND more than you GET BACK, you're in DEBT! 😴
That's when you feel tired.

If you GET BACK more than you SPEND, you're in PROFIT! ⚡
That's when you feel excited and ready for more!

💡 FINANCIAL TIP
Check your diary: What activities give you the BEST return?
Invest MORE in those! That's smart learning finance!


