🔬 WHAT MAKES YOU CURIOUS? (PATTERN SPOTTING)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

Look through your notes and ask:

📌 What appears AGAIN and AGAIN?

Do you keep asking about:
• Space? 🌌
• Animals? 🦋
• How things work? ⚙️
• Stories? 📖
• Numbers? 🔢
• Colors? 🌈

If you see the SAME topic popping up, that's a PATTERN!
That's what NATURALLY makes you curious! 🎯

📌 What colors show up when you're curious?

If it's always 🟡 Yellow (curiosity) + 🔵 Blue (thinking),
you might be a RESEARCHER type!

If it's always 🟡 Yellow + 🟠 Orange (chaos),
you might be an EXPLORER type!

If it's always 🟡 Yellow + 🟢 Green (growth),
you might be a GROWER type!

Your COLOR PATTERN tells you HOW you learn best!


