🚫 WHAT YOU NATURALLY DISLIKE
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

Your diary will ALSO show what you DON'T like! 

Look for:
📌 Patterns of AVOIDING
Are there topics you NEVER write about?
Are there activities that keep getting skipped?

📌 Patterns of LOW ENERGY
When do you write 😴 or 💤?
What were you doing right before?
What colors were around?

📌 Patterns of CLASHING
When do you write 💥 or ⚡ with homies?
What colors were involved?
Was it the same colors every time?

If you see a DISLIKE pattern, that's useful too!
It tells you: "This isn't for me. That's OK!" ✅

You don't have to like everything. Your diary helps you find YOUR path!


